title: Tales of Greenwich - Micah "Bam Bamm" White
description: One of our funniest episodes ever. Micah "Bam Bamm" White tells us about his travels to Connecticut with Matt, we also talk about the Venom GT, chicken fisting, fearless armenians, video production, and the Miami Heat.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
